# M6 P07 — slipstream movement-after-countdown test.
#
# User reported "stuck in the platform" on slipstream. Validate by:
#   1. Spawning into slipstream FFA (host).
#   2. Capturing the spawn (during COUNTDOWN, input locked).
#   3. After COUNTDOWN releases, hold RIGHT and capture motion.
#
# If the mech moves visibly between the press-right frame and the
# later frames, "stuck" was just the COUNTDOWN input-lock; if it
# stays put, there's a real spawn-trap to fix.

window 1280 720
seed 1 0
out build/shots/m6_slipstream_move
network host 24710
name HostA
loadout - "Pulse Rifle" "Sidearm" Light Standard
map slipstream
no_parallax

# Wait through lobby (~60 ticks) + countdown (~60 ticks).
# COUNTDOWN finishes around tick 120, then ACTIVE.
at 100 shot pre_countdown
at 130 shot countdown
at 160 shot just_active
at 180 press right
at 200 shot moving_t20
at 240 shot moving_t60
at 280 shot moving_t100
at 320 release right
at 340 shot stopped

at 400 end

contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 320 180
